WEBVTT


00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.200
As a mother of four, I know a good toy when I see it.

00:00:02.201 --> 00:00:04.481
This car has it all. It has a five point harness for safety

00:00:04.482 --> 00:00:07.481
and he's actually pretty fast for a small little kid's toy.

00:00:07.482 --> 00:00:08.681
My son is seven years old,

00:00:08.682 --> 00:00:09.801
but he's more the size of an eight year old.

00:00:09.802 --> 00:00:11.881
So he's very tall and he fits in this perfectly.

00:00:11.882 --> 00:00:14.261
This hits any bumps on our property,

00:00:14.400 --> 00:00:17.200
takes him like a champ. If you're looking for a ride on vehicle

00:00:17.201 --> 00:00:18.641
and you have an uneven backyard,

00:00:18.642 --> 00:00:20.401
this rides on grass perfectly.

00:00:20.402 --> 00:00:22.001
In any other terrain, sand,

00:00:22.002 --> 00:00:25.041
rocks, this actually is true four wheel drive.

00:00:25.042 --> 00:00:26.721
Look at this thing pick up some speed.

00:00:26.722 --> 00:00:29.781
I've had so much fun on this and I would recommend it to anybody.
